&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://imgur.com/zvLzrAm">How to Realign Higanbana&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Leveling Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/leveling-guide/</link><pubDate>Wed, 06 Aug 2025 01:31:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/leveling-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="level-50">Level 50&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3et8">Level 50 Opener&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Rotate through your combos and smash that Midare button. Use Meikyo for Gekko and Kasha past the opener. Refresh Higanbana as close to 0 as possible.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="level-52">Level 52&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Introduces Kenki Gauge and Hissatsu: Shinten. Use it when you want and be sure not to overcap.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="level-60">Level 60&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://ffxivrotations.com/3lvo">Level 60 Opener&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Once you begin accruing Kenki to spend on Shinten, the opener should look like this.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Basic Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:52:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="foreword">Foreword&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>As of Dawntrail, Samurai has been part of the game for seven years. As part of the team, I am updating this guide for Dawntrail as we have gotten a substantial amount of changes upon release, until 7.05 which marked a big shift in gameplay since Shadowbringers, and will be covered in this document. This guide is intended for newer and older players alike.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>-Zheng&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>The following section summarizes Samurai’s abilities. You may also refer to &lt;a href="https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/jobguide/samurai/">Square Enix’s Samurai Job Guide&lt;/a> for specific skill and trait text. Feel free to skip this section if you are familiar with Samurai’s skills.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Skills Overview</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:48:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="samurai-skills-overview">Samurai Skills Overview&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="global-cooldown-actions-single-target">Global Cooldown Actions (Single Target)&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th style="text-align: left">Icon&lt;/th>
 &lt;th style="text-align: left">Name&lt;/th>
 &lt;th style="text-align: left">Description&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
